oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Hank Williams Lost Notebooks cover
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Williams, Hank, 1923-1953; Sound recordings -- Album covers;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color card (red, black and yellow on yellow) announcing the Lost Notebooks of Hank Williams 2011 album cover. Album features unfinished songs that Williams never recorded and completed by others including Alan Jackson, Norah Jones, John White, Lucinda Williams, Vince Gill, Rodney Crowell, Patty Loveless, Holly Williams, Levon Helm, Jakob Dylan, Sheryl Crow and Merle Haggard.
